  "lyrics": "Yeah! Did he hear it? Motherfucker! I think he can. Shit. Ayy, I come from Mckenna's and I come from L.A. And I took you on your mind And I did some damn Don't worry about it, don't judge me I'm just sittin' in your back pocket Lovely, now in a seat in your seat Sittin' there with smoke still through You can't be brave Sittin' in the back, looking at you like What are you doing? Get in your mind when you come with me It's just a fucking design, it's just a fucking crime Can't do nothing over the left You gotta fuck with me I gotta get your best Ayy, don't you know that you just can't beat me? I'm sorry That it Deceives you But you ain't up I said, are you ready? Go Fuck with the duck I've been taught that you don't run I've been taught Could've been a son of a bitch, but I've been saved You're just a bitch sitting there with nothing more With your head cocked up and your head in the A Don't you see you're a piece of shit? Fuck off with that Fuck off with me Last time you fucked with me Ayy Simon, you're a tough Get your shit popped This motherfucker Get the fuck off Ayy Shoot up on him if you want to Fuck your life if you want to You knew it better than that You little lady son of a bitch You don't like that Now you know Oh, how I feel I said, now, now, now you know How I really Feel It's your deal And you're gone And you're gone And you're gone And you're gone And you're gone And you're gone Out the door, bitch Bye Oh Fuck I'll save you Bitch Bitch  Press 1 Somebody Give A fuck",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 1.2599999904632568,
      "text": "Yeah!",
      "start": 0.7400000095367432
    },
    {
      "end": 4,
      "text": "Did he hear it?",
      "start": 3
    },
    {
      "end": 5.760000228881836,
      "text": "Motherfucker!",
      "start": 5.239999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 8.020000457763672,
      "text": "I think he can.",
      "start": 6.920000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 9.180000305175781,
      "text": "Shit.",
      "start": 8.699999809265137
    },
    {
      "end": 13,
      "text": "Ayy, I come from Mckenna's and I come from L.A.",
      "start": 10.0600004196167
    },
    {
      "end": 14.260000228881836,
      "text": "And I took you on your mind",
      "start": 13.100000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 15.539999961853027,
      "text": "And I did some damn",
      "start": 14.260000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 18.31999969482422,
      "text": "Don't worry about it, don't judge me",
      "start": 15.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 19.940000534057617,
      "text": "I'm just sittin' in your back pocket",
      "start": 18.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 22.81999969482422,
      "text": "Lovely, now in a seat in your seat",
      "start": 20.100000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 24.6200008392334,
      "text": "Sittin' there with smoke still through",
      "start": 22.920000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 25.600000381469727,
      "text": "You can't be brave",
      "start": 24.6200008392334
    },
    {
      "end": 27.899999618530273,
      "text": "Sittin' in the back, looking at you like",
      "start": 25.719999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 30,
      "text": "What are you doing?",
      "start": 27.899999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 32.439998626708984,
      "text": "Get in your mind when you come with me",
      "start": 30.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 35.119998931884766,
      "text": "It's just a fucking design, it's just a fucking crime",
      "start": 32.439998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 37.2599983215332,
      "text": "Can't do nothing over the left",
      "start": 35.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 38.5,
      "text": "You gotta fuck with me",
      "start": 37.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 39.939998626708984,
      "text": "I gotta get your best",
      "start": 38.5
    },
    {
      "end": 44.380001068115234,
      "text": "Ayy, don't you know that you just can't beat me?",
      "start": 39.939998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 46.31999969482422,
      "text": "I'm sorry",
      "start": 45.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 47.34000015258789,
      "text": "That it",
      "start": 46.380001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 49.02000045776367,
      "text": "Deceives you",
      "start": 47.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 50.97999954223633,
      "text": "But you ain't up",
      "start": 49.02000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 53.459999084472656,
      "text": "I said, are you ready?",
      "start": 51.220001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 54.70000076293945,
      "text": "Go",
      "start": 54.380001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 56.20000076293945,
      "text": "Fuck with the duck",
      "start": 54.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 58.380001068115234,
      "text": "I've been taught that you don't run",
      "start": 56.20000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 59.599998474121094,
      "text": "I've been taught",
      "start": 58.599998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 61.939998626708984,
      "text": "Could've been a son of a bitch, but I've been saved",
      "start": 59.599998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 64.4000015258789,
      "text": "You're just a bitch sitting there with nothing more",
      "start": 61.939998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 66.94000244140625,
      "text": "With your head cocked up and your head in the A",
      "start": 64.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 69.36000061035156,
      "text": "Don't you see you're a piece of shit?",
      "start": 66.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 70.62000274658203,
      "text": "Fuck off with that",
      "start": 69.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 71.86000061035156,
      "text": "Fuck off with me",
